<plot>The young rookie cop Jacob is learning the rules on the street from his older partner Michael, but Jacob has a difficult time separating his ideals from the work. In the area they patrol, a young boy has been attacked the night before and everybody is affected by the meaningless crime. When the case coincidentally ends up at the two cops' desk, Jacob finds himself in a situation where his beliefs are put to the ultimate test.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422088</url></doc>
